#. <section class="sutta" id="sn46.77-88"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.77-88:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.77-88:0.2"
msgid "9. Gaṅgāpeyyālavagga"
msgstr "9. Abbreviated Texts on the Ganges"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 77–​88. Gaṅgānadīādisutta → gaṅgādisuttāni (bj)
msgctxt "sn46.77-88:0.3"
msgid "77–​88. Gaṅgānadīādisutta"
msgstr "77–88. The Ganges River, Etc."

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.77-88:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gaṅgā nadī pācīnaninnā pācīnapoṇā pācīnapabbhārā;"
msgstr "“Mendicants, the Ganges river slants, slopes, and inclines to the east."

msgctxt "sn46.77-88:1.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satta bojjhaṅge bhāvento satta bojjhaṅge "
"bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a mendicant who develops and cultivates the seven awakening "
"factors slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment."

msgctxt "sn46.77-88:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satta bojjhaṅge bhāvento satta bojjhaṅge "
"bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a mendicant who develops the seven awakening factors slant, "
"slope, and incline to extinguishment?"

msgctxt "sn46.77-88:1.4"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti … pe … "
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ "
"vossaggapariṇāmiṃ …"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the awakening factors of mindfulness, "
"investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and "
"equanimity, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen "
"as letting go."

msgctxt "sn46.77-88:1.5"
msgid ""
"evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satta bojjhaṅge bhāvento satta bojjhaṅge "
"bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a mendicant who develops and cultivates the seven awakening "
"factors slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment.”"

msgctxt "sn46.77-88:1.6"
msgid "(Yāva esanā pāḷi vitthāretabbā.)"
msgstr "(To be expanded for each of the different rivers as in SN 45.91–102.)"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.77-88:1.7"
msgid "Gaṅgāpeyyālavaggo navamo."
msgstr ""

